# Global Superstore Sales Analysis Dashboard

## Overview

This project presents a comprehensive sales and profitability analysis of the Global Superstore dataset using Microsoft Excel. The dashboard transforms raw transactional data into meaningful business insights through data analysis, Pivot Tables, Pivot Charts, and KPI visualizations.

The objective of this project is to identify key sales trends, profitable regions, top-performing products, and customer shipping preferences to support data-driven decision-making.

---

## Dashboard Preview


---

## Dataset Information

The Global Superstore dataset contains worldwide retail sales transactions and includes information such as:

* Orders
* Sales
* Profit
* Shipping Costs
* Products
* Categories
* Countries
* Regions
* Customer Segments
* Order Dates

