## Dashboard Features

### Sales Performance Analysis

* Total Sales Overview
* Year-wise Sales Trend Analysis (2011–2014)

### Profitability Analysis

* High Profit Countries
* Most Profitable Regions

### Product Analysis

* Top Selling Products Across the World
* Product Performance Comparison

### Logistics Analysis

* Most Preferred Shipping Modes
* Global Shipping Cost Overview

### Executive KPIs

* Total Sales
* Total Profit
* Shipping Cost
* Top Selling Product

---

## Key Insights

### Sales Growth

Sales demonstrated a consistent upward trend between 2011 and 2014, indicating steady business growth.

### Regional Performance

APAC, EU, and US regions generated the highest profits among all markets.

### Product Performance

Apple Smart Phone (Full Size) emerged as the top-selling product globally.

### Shipping Preferences

Standard Class accounted for approximately 60% of all shipments, making it the most preferred shipping mode.

### Country Performance

Countries such as the United States, China, India, United Kingdom, and Mexico contributed significantly to overall profits.

